properties.Name: Riot
properties.Agents: consecutive nightly riots, crowd aiming to get to Mr. Pitt's house to pull it down, but kept off by the military. The Duchess of Gloucester was in great danger, returning from the circus; she was pursued by the mob, crying no Royalty, no Pitt, till she got very near to her own house'
